channel.title: Chaotics 317 delta
channel.description: Hello every1 i have added chaotics to my server i added the models gzipped, and added the ints, plus i have added the item in item.cfg but when i spawn it my account crushes and it wont let me log in again. whats the mistake i have done :S please help me. and if this is stupid for some of u, im verry sorry since its my first time in adding models :( thanks alot for whoever helps me.

item.title: Chaotics 317 delta
item.dc:creator: @Ace1 Ace.
item.description:
@Ace1 wrote:

Go ingame, type the following into your chat box in-game.
add models (drop model id here: example 14030)
add models (wield model id here: example 14031)

Make sure you type it all in correctly. In this case, you should be typing:
add models 14030
add models 14031

On some clients, you will disconnect, that is completely normal. Its just refreshing the client in a way.

Once you have done the add models stuff, spawn your item and problem should be solved.

Best of luck buddy.
